iv class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12 "><p>Date :<strong>{{data.arnDate}}</strong></p></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12 text-right"><span><strong>Name of Authorized Signatory </strong></span><p>{{data.authName}}</p><span><strong>Designation / Status </strong></span><p>{{data.auth_dg}}</p></div> <div style="font-weight: bold;"><span style=" text-decoration: underline;">Note:</span> <span>To see the latest updated system computed GSTIN turnover and AATO on the PAN,Dashboard screen can be referred for the same.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>',
